title: Fuel Cell Electric Vehicles

description:
In this episode, the team discusses fuel cell electric vehicles with Senior Engineering Manager of the Fuel Cell Integration Group at Toyota Motor North America Research and Development, Jackie Birdsall.

Follow Jackie on Twitter @Jackie_Birdsall and find her on LinkedIn.
